'''玛乌戈扎塔·舒莫夫斯卡''' ({{lang-pl|Małgorzata Szumowska}}，{{IPA-pl|mawɡɔˈʐata ʂuˈmɔfska|lang}}; 1973年2月26日-) 是一名[[波蘭|波蘭]]女性電影導演。她2013年的作品《{{link-pl|以慾望之名|W imię...}}》於[[第63屆柏林電影節|第63屆柏林影展]]獲得[[泰迪熊獎|泰迪熊獎]]<ref name="Berlin">{{Cite web |url=http://www.berlinale.de/en/presse/pressemitteilungen/alle/Alle-Detail_16724.html |title=Berlinale 2013: Competition Now Complete |accessdate=2013-02-08 |work=berlinale |archive-date=2013-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130410152015/https://www.berlinale.de/en/presse/pressemitteilungen/alle/Alle-Detail_16724.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="asiaone">{{Cite web |url=http://www.asiaone.com/News/Latest%2BNews/Showbiz/Story/A1Story20130208-401125.html |title=Polish gay priest drama launches Berlin film fest race |accessdate=2013-02-08 |work=asiaone |archive-date=2020-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929184124/https://www.asiaone.com/News/Latest%2BNews/Showbiz/Story/A1Story20130208-401125.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>；2015年，她以《{{link-pl|通靈診療室|Body/Ciało}}》於[[第65屆柏林影展|第65屆柏林影展]]獲得[[最佳導演銀熊獎|最佳導演銀熊獎]]。<ref name="65Berlin">{{cite web |url=http://www.berlinale.de/en/presse/pressemitteilungen/wettbewerb/wettbewerb-presse-detail_26454.html |title=Jafar Panahi’s New Film in Competition |accessdate=28 January 2015 |work=berlinale.de |archive-date=2015-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150124060215/http://www.berlinale.de/en/presse/pressemitteilungen/wettbewerb/wettbewerb-presse-detail_26454.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

